 training that simulate security and privacy incidents.', N'Practical exercises may include, for example, no-notice social engineering attempts to collect information, gain unauthorized access, or simulate the adverse impact of opening malicious email attachments or invoking, via spear phishing attacks, malicious web links. Privacy-related practical exercises may include, for example, practice modules with quizzes on handling personally identifiable information and affected individuals in various scenarios.', N'Awareness and Training', N'Literacy Training and Awareness', 0, NULL, N'RAC', NULL, NULL, NULL, 63, NULL, NULL)
